<a href="http://www.ed.gov/teachers/needs/speced/adhd/adhd-resource-pt2.pdf">Teaching Children with Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder: Instructional Strategies and Practices</a> 
<img border="0" src="../../../images/pdficon_small.gif" width="15" height="19" alt="pdf icon" /></h4>
<p>
Publication from U.S. Department of Education (2004)
</p>

