<a href="http://www.commonwealthfund.org/publications/publications_show.htm?doc_id=605625">Developmental Screening in Primary Care: The Effectiveness of Current Practice and Recommendations for Improvement</a></h4>
<p>
Report from the Commonwealth Fund on developmental screenings by pediatricians and other primary care providers (2007)
</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.nces.ed.gov/ecls/">Early Childhood Longitudinal Study</a></h4>
<p>
Study providing national data on children at birth through the eighth grade
</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.acf.hhs.gov/programs/opre/hs/impact_study/">Head Start Impact Study</a></h4>
<p>
Study conducted beginning in 2000 through 2009 to determine impact of Head Start on children it serves
</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.tacommunities.org/community/view/id/1008">Identification Part C Community</a></h4>
<p>
Information from OSEP Community of Practice on identification of at-risk infants and toddlers
</p>
<h4><a href="http://ecrp.uiuc.edu/v4n1/marcon.html">Moving Up the Grades: Relationship between Preschool Model and Later School Success</a></h4>
<p>
Follow-up study on effect of preschool model on later school success conducted by the University of Florida (2002)
</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.sri.com/neils/index.html">National Early Intervention Longitudinal Study</a></h4>
<p>
Web site with reports and publications from national study of children with disabilities and their families in early intervention into elementary school
</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.tacommunities.org/community/view/id/1028">Preschool LRE-Part B/619 Community
</a> </h4>
<p>
Information from OSEP Community of Practice on placement in the least restrictive environment in the preschool setting
</p>
<h4>
<a href="http://www.dec-sped.org/pdf/positionpapers/Prmtg_Pos_Outcomes_Companion_Paper.pdf">Promoting Positive Outcomes for Children with Disabilities: Recommendations for Curriculum, Assessment, and Program Evaluation</a>
<img border="0" src="../../../images/pdficon_small.gif" width="15" height="15" alt="pdf icon" /></h4>
