<h4><a href="http://www.tacommunities.org/community/view/id/1029">Settings Part C Community</a> </h4>
<p>
Materials and resources from OSEP Community of Practice on natural environments practices and supports
</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.gao.gov/new.items/d02394.pdf">Special Education: Grant Programs Designed to Serve Children Ages 0-5</a> <img border="0" src="../../../images/pdficon_small.gif" width="15" height="15" alt="pdf icon" /></h4>
<p>
Report from the General Accountability Office (GAO) on early childhood education and care programs under IDEA (2002)
</p>

