A sourcebook of effective family-school-community partnerships developed by CADRE (2003)
</p>
<h4><a href="http://www.ncpie.org/pubs/AdviceEngagingFamilies.pdf">Engaging Families to Improve Achievement: Advice from the Research</a> <img border="0" src="../../../images/pdficon_small.gif" width="15" height="15" alt="pdf icon" /></h4>
